title: Grim.Dawn.Alpha.v0.1.8.2(B12)
description:
This is the new build. HAS NOT BEEN PROPERLY CRACKED but the original gamefiles are intact. Files ending in ORG are the ones replaced by the crack. Found these from the cs.rin.ru forum. Included luma emu files and a pack created for b9 that was working. Hopefully someone finds a crack soon.


As with anything you download from untrusted sources use at your own risk...Comodo didn't pick anything up.

Thanks to Demde and JBeckman for original upload :)
